143
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:12,080
If something unfavorable happens,

144
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,540
please call here.

145
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:17,080
Thank you.

146
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:20,430
<i>[Yoo San Woo, CEO]</i>

147
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:22,530
