179
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:02,240
That man... my uncle... What on earth...

180
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:07,620
Uncle, what's wrong?

181
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:12,810
I have the same symptoms. If I shed a tear after seeing a woman for the first time,

182
