191
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:51,990
<i>If a person close to you suddenly buys many items, be suspicious.</i>

192
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:56,680
<i>Other symptoms include...</i>

193
00:14:56,680 --> 00:15:00,540
